wheellllll.license

类 License

  • java.lang.Object
    • wheellllll.license.License

  • public class License
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provide two license functions, capacity and throughput.

    • 嵌套类概要

      嵌套类 
      限定符和类型 类和说明
      static class  License.Availability
      Enum for availability.

      Enum for license functional type.
      static class  License.TimeUnit
      Enum for time unit, every enum has a value. value of MILLISECONDS set to 1, other unit value set to the ratio of itself and millisecond.

      • enableCapacity

        public void enableCapacity(int capacityLimit,
                           boolean maintain)
        Enable the capacity function.
        参数:
        capacityLimit - Limit value for capacity
        maintain - This value reflect whether continue from the old place. If set as true, the initial capacity value will be set to previous capacity value, otherwise it will be set to 0

      • enableThroughput

        public void enableThroughput(int throughputLimit,
                             boolean maintain,
                             License.TimeUnit timeUnit)
        Enable the throughput function.
        参数:
        throughputLimit - Limit value for throughput
        maintain - This value reflect whether continue from the old place. If set as true, the initial throughput value will be set to previous throughput value, otherwise it will be set to 0
        timeUnit - Time unit for throughput function

      • use

        public License.Availability use()
        This method is called where license usage is needed.
        返回:
        Availability represent whether the license is still available. AVAILABLE represent it is available, CAPACITYEXCEEDED represent capacity reaches limit, THROUGHPUTEXCEEDED represent throughput reaches limit, BOTHEXCEEDED represent both reaches limit.
        另请参阅:
        License.Availability

      • reset

        public void reset(License.LicenseType type)
        Reset the current license value.
        参数:
        type - Type of this license. If type is LicenseType.BOTH, both capacity value and throughput value will be set to 0, otherwise the chosen target will be set to 0.
